Extract a table of pipeline IDs and property values

deal_pipelines.Rd

Extract a table of pipeline IDs and property values

deal_pipelines(pipelines = get_deal_pipelines())

Arguments

pipelines

A list of pipelines from get_deal_pipelines

Value

A tibble of deal pipelines

Examples

deal_pipes <- deal_pipelines()
